            <h2 class="if-you">Welcome to our website, we want to inform you about its structure.
                The site consists of 2 parts, the first for getting acquainted with the sights, the second for
                information.
            </h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="welcome_buttons">
        <button class="wel_but" type="submit" value="">go to info</button>
        <button class="wel_but" type="submit" value="">go tourism</button>
    </div>
</div>
